data.description: Beautiful 2 bedroom Immaculate house with a double car garage  in a very nice area of Los Angeles near Sofi Stadium close to freeways,airport,shopping areas and much more.Property has an extra good size shed that can be used as an extra bonus room for your guest or storage.This property has a good size lot with lots of potential to add or to convert garage into an ADU.Buyer and agent to check with city for requirements.This house is a must see to appreciate all the amenities it has to offer.
